<span id="freeTextContainer1229219831698548399">Overall, I liked it, however I wasn&apos;t totally enthralled. I&apos;m not sure what exactly was missing for me, but I wasn&apos;t able to really connect with the characters and the story. Still enjoyable, but wishing I didn&apos;t feel so detached while reading it.</span>
  <span id="freeText1229219831698548399" style="display:none">Overall, I liked it, however I wasn't totally enthralled. I'm not sure what exactly was missing for me, but I wasn't able to really connect with the characters and the story. Still enjoyable, but wishing I didn't feel so detached while reading it.</span>
