<div id="review_1936052513" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1936052513" />
    <a title="Maria Espadinha" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/20749430-maria-espadinha"><img alt="Maria Espadinha" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1595262289p2/20749430.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1936052513?book_show_action=true">Aug 14, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Maria Espadinha" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Maria Espadinha" href="/user/show/20749430-maria-espadinha">Maria Espadinha</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1936052513" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16441404620574509064">The Hitchcockian Muse Strikes Again<br/><br/><br/>Purity attracts Evil in the same way Protons attract Electrons. <br/>It’s all about Balance and Opposites Attraction!<br/><br/>Hence, it was definitely not surprising watching a good girl like Mary Yellan gradually merging into deep dark waters 😈. However, there’s nothing to worry about cos, in due time, this lack of surprise will be generously compensated! 😉<br/><br/>Patience and Fortitude, cos... Du Maurier the Hitchcockian Muse... always delivers! 👍👍👍😍</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

